{code}
  if ("leave".equalsIgnoreCase(argv[idx])) {
      action = HdfsConstants.SafeModeAction.SAFEMODE_LEAVE;
{code}

[~stevel@apache.org] and [~walter.k.su] do you think so..?

Hi [~stevel@apache.org]. I think {{String.equalsIgnoreCase()}} is pretty safe.
